		<div id="correspondentContent" class="expandingContent" style="display:none">
		
<table>
<tr>
<td class="column1"><span class="authors"><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/daniel-akst/" class="author" >Daniel Akst</a></span><span class="shortBlurb">Journalist, novelist</span></td>

<td class="column2"><span class="authors"><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/yoni-appelbaum/" class="author" >Yoni Appelbaum</a></span><span class="shortBlurb">Writer and historian</span></td>

